sourcesContent: import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { MDBContainer, MDBNavbar, MDBNavbarBrand, MDBNavbarToggler, MDBIcon, MDBNavbarNav, MDBNavbarItem, MDBNavbarLink, MDBBtn, MDBDropdown, MDBDropdownToggle, MDBDropdownMenu, MDBDropdownItem, MDBDropdownLink, MDBCollapse, MDBCardImage, MDBCarouselInner, MDBCarouselItem, MDBCarouselElement, MDBCard, MDBCardBody, MDBCardTitle, MDBCardText, MDBRow, MDBCol } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit'; import axios from 'axios'; import Swal from 'sweetalert2'; import Cookies from 'js-cookie'; import { reactLocalStorage } from 'reactjs-localstorage'; function NavBar() { const [showBasic, setShowBasic] = useState(false); const [showNavRight, setShowNavRight] = useState(false); return (  Wellness -HealthCare setShowBasic(!showBasic)} > Home About Us Login Registration ) }; export default NavBar;
